OL,3,GYorkshire & Humber
OL,4,
OL,5,CSaturday:FA chilly and bright start.
OL,6,FHowever, cloud will increase from the
OL,7,Fwest to bring some outbreaks of rain
OL,8,Facross all parts from mid-afternoon,
OL,9,Fclearing overnight. Breezy.
OL,10,
OL,11,COutlook for Sunday to Tuesday:FDrier
OL,12,Fand brighter on Sunday, with some
OL,13,Fshowers late in the day. Dry with
OL,14,Fvariable cloud and sunny spells
OL,15,FMonday. Wet and windy conditions
OL,16,Fspread east Tuesday. Temperatures near
OL,17,Faverage.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
